The SOS Call button lets you instantly summon emergency help from SiriusXM Guardian Customer Care. When you press it, the system:

* Places a call to an SOS operator (with a 10‑second delay that can be cancelled);
* Sends the vehicle’s basic data (make, model) and its last‑known GPS coordinates;
* Opens a voice link so the operator can speak with the occupants and hear sounds inside the vehicle;
* Allows the operator to contact emergency responders and share the vehicle’s location and other relevant information;
* Keeps the connection active until the operator ends it, and can be cancelled at any time by pressing the button again or using the cancel control on the touchscreen.
